-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 [ description ]
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* lightweight tcp proxy firewall for bbs telnet connections
* runs anywhere node.js runs!

* features:
*   - per-ip concurrent connection limiting
*   - http redirect server (port 80)
*   - geo/ip country blocking (maxmind geolite2)
*   - ip whitelist and blocklist (supports cidr)
*   - rate limiting / flood protection
*   - optional ssh server with legacy cipher support
*   - utf-8 / cp437 encoding detection and routing

